			<h1 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.05;font-size:clamp(36px,5.6vw,60px);margin:18px 0 20px;color:#F6F4EF;">Give your work <em style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;color:#DFFF00;">a foundation</em> to stand on.</h1>
			<p style="font-size:18px;color:#F6F4EF;max-width:52ch;margin:0 auto 30px;opacity:0.82;">Nine curated interaction modules, from grid reveals to case-study transitions to scroll-tied sequences, built only for portfolio and case-study sites. Nothing you'd need Framer for. Nothing you don't.</p>
